i
\mu\left(A\right)=\sum_{i}p_{i}\mu_{i}\left(A\right)=\sum_{i}p_{i}\sum_{j}\mu_{i}\left(A_{j}\right)=\sum_{i}\sum_{j}p_{i}\mu_{i}\left(A_{j}\right)=\sum_{j}\sum_{i}p_{i}\mu_{i}\left(A_{j}\right)=\sum_{j}\mu\left(A_{j}\right)
